Package humandeque

Class HumanDeque

java.lang.Object
java.util.AbstractCollection<E>
java.util.ArrayDeque<Human>
humandeque.HumanDeque
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Cloneable, Iterable<Human>, Collection<Human>, Deque<Human>, Queue<Human>
public class HumanDeque extends ArrayDeque<Human>
Represents a collection of human objects and associated metadata. This class extends the ArrayDeque class and adds a creation time field to track when the collection was created.
